                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Welcome to 10X Health!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;My name is Heidi Rubio, and I will be your dedicated wellness concierge and my role is to help facilitate your growth and success within the 10X Health System.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Moving forward, &lt;strong&gt;I will be your primary contact&lt;/strong&gt; and liaison between you and the medical team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ll check in with you frequently to ensure you are getting the most out of your program and that all of your questions have been addressed and answered.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Next Steps&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Review treatment instructions&lt;/u&gt;. Our medical coordinator will send you an email regarding your medical instructions. If you feel you need further instruction, we can schedule a face-to-face tutorial with a member of our medical team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Follow-up labs&lt;/u&gt;. Your next set of lab work will be due &lt;strong&gt;6-8 weeks&lt;/strong&gt; after starting your program. This step ensures that your hormones are being optimized and you are feeling your best.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Of course, feel free to call me with questions anytime throughout your journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;Congratulations on taking this big step for you and your health. I look forward to guiding you on your path to a happy, healthier you.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Yours in good health,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Heidi Rubio&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Wellness Concierge&lt;br /&gt;
10&lt;span style=&quot;color:#c0392b;&quot;&gt;X &lt;/span&gt;Health&lt;br /&gt;
Direct: 786.388.0707&lt;br /&gt;
Main: 305.682.1818 ext.374&lt;br /&gt;
Fax: 786.598.8612&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://10xhealthsystem.com/&quot;&gt;10xhealthsystem.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
